NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Much of this, of course, was out of NBCUniversal's control.\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2108, \"end\": 2120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 0.9999999994993232, \"rank\": 5.006587138180212e-10, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tokyo Games were delayed a year because of the coronavirus pandemic and the run-up to those Games was joyless given the state of the world.\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2275, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Complicating matters was the time zone - Tokyo is 13 hours ahead of the East Coast of the United States.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2317, \"end\": 2322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999965894, \"rank\": 1.8445774928038885e-12, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2366, \"end\": 2379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9987984651087568, \"rank\": 0.0009423685644786743, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I see Paris as a chance for the Olympics to get its mojo back,\\\" Bob Costas, who hosted NBC's prime-time Olympics coverage 11 times, toldThe Athleticin February.\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2389, \"end\": 2394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997406094162, \"rank\": 2.5939059340708073e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2470, \"end\": 2473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 0.999578332577083, \"rank\": 0.0002159511742990921, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The real problem \\u2026 came with the two COVID Olympics, one of which was postponed.\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the absence of crowds and family and friends on hand, a lot of things that make the Olympics a great television show were missing.\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The absence of crowds for any sports event diminishes it greatly.\\\"\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo: BERTRAND GUAY / AFP via Getty Images)  Spot the pattern.\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2862, \"end\": 2867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9999999653070978, \"rank\": 2.1563467254563314e-08, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Connect the terms  Find the hidden link between sports terms  Play today's puzzle\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2976, \"entities\": []}]}"